GG Crash bandicoot Jungle
============
By FireWavezZ
-------------

This map is made because i truely love(d) the game Crash Bandicoot on PS1. i played it alot back in the day so i tried to remake it a little on this gg map.

ive been working a full day getting the textures right, eventually i only used half of the textures that i made.
might upload them all as a pack if i decide to.

well hope you enjoy it, please leave feedback if you played and ifyou would like to see more CB maps :]
thanks!

(CB means Crash Bandicoot but the name is soo long lol)
